.SH STANDARDS
None.
.SH HISTORY
Similar to a call in SVr4.
.SH BUGS
.BR profil ()
cannot be used on a program that also uses
.B ITIMER_PROF
interval timers (see
.BR setitimer (2)).
.P
True kernel profiling provides more accurate results.
